text: The Tagalog Wikipedia is the Tagalog version of the online encyclopedia, Wikipedia. It was started on December 1, 2003. In 2011, it had reached over 50,000 articles. It is 68th largest edition by article count. It has over 51,000 articles and is the 51st largest Wikipedia according to the number of articles as of May 31, 2011. ==References== ==Other websites== *wikt:en:Category:Tagalog language *oldwikisource:Category:Tagalog Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2003
